{"tid":1230894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為海外學生 我衷心希望同香港人講聲 多謝","createTime":"2019-06-16T10:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T11:10:15.000Z","uid":7401,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea2c505c6c480e866ee75338b585efcb27737240","tid":1230894,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"身處海外嘅自己 面對住大考 無嘢可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初以為香港已經變成只講利益嘅地方<br />\n今日，或者呢幾日<br />\n見到眾議員(特別係鄺sir)、眾市民、First aid、物資、記者同埋前線義士<br />\n實在係令到身處海外嘅我地非常感動<br />\n我地一樣會同大家並肩作戰<br />\n繼續影響同感化身邊嘅人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油！謹記我地嘅目標！唔好比短暫勝利沖昏頭腦！<br />\n徹回！反送中！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保護屬於我地嘅香港！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpAQkst.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpAQkst.png&h=bd2eb7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片Credit to 痴肥豬肉佬"},{"pid":"5940633a25f23083cff2bd01ddf87e3bd621149e","tid":1230894,"uid":7401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"亦希望梁先生可以Rest in peace <br />\n辛苦了...其他人都一定要撐住！<br />\n有需要一定要搵人傾訴、求助！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b828fee779cdc569de7b2fa21a4512803aadd759","tid":1230894,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"點睇去佔禮賓府？"},{"pid":"9891db42338a35969cc5b632cb53ac96f589d28d","tid":1230894,"uid":107693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"人在異地，好恨自己唔係現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未見過香港咁團結，香港人加油!!"},{"pid":"8df94b3e10c965752167e5d9313aad10b1cacc65","tid":1230894,"uid":7401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9891db42